author=Amkush
description=Native Zygisk virtual camera — hooks Camera3Device::processCaptureResult in cameraserver via ShadowHook to inject synthetic frames from any video/image source. Works across all OEM devices (Qualcomm / MediaTek / Exynos). Bypasses Java-level Camera1/2/X hooks.
